### Parse protobuf source file to AST

I have already passed all official tests. If you like to run your own tests, just follow this code blow:

```
$ node test.js
```

If you need to see the structure of AST, just add a log [Here](https://github.com/yyfrankyy/protobuf.pegjs/blob/master/test.js#L23).

```
console.log(util.inspect(protoTree))
```

Thanks to [PEGJS](https://github.com/dmajda/pegjs) and its [example](https://github.com/dmajda/pegjs/blob/master/examples/javascript.pegjs) of parsing JavaScript(ES5)

Feel free to contact me [@yyfrankyy](//github.com/yyfrankyy) .
